{"tid":2422239,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"議員質疑為何不許市民取用強積金　陳茂波稱需謹慎處理","createTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T07:13:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b932d6e2cd921f24218815989f593c8629ca66","tid":2422239,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577433-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577433-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFXd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=07a24651\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577433-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b303c721\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577433-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波到立法會財委會簡介財政預算案。有議員對當局不願意設立失業援助金表示失望，又關注「百分百擔保個人特惠貸款計劃」細節。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波回應說，當局研判隨住本港的防疫工作見成效，亦正推展市民廣泛接種疫苗，外圍如歐美正安排接種疫苗，他估計經濟動力會在年中開始好轉，屆時失業壓力會緩減。<br />\n<br />\n有議員質詢為何不容許市民取用強積金款項，認為用強積金作擔保是較為合適。陳茂波強調強積金是市民的退休保障，即使個別人士出現財政困難，債權人亦不能動用他的退休保障，認為要謹慎處理。當局設立「百分百擔保個人特惠貸款計劃」，是給予市民多一個選項。"},{"pid":"23c002215d020599a91d66316cb47b806662b3b6","tid":2422239,"uid":108016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:09:06.000Z","msg":"驚BNO拎錢走嘛"},{"pid":"292da30e165e98a5f8ab0b9644433602766aa1bf","tid":2422239,"uid":166474,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"老闆對沖強積金又唔洗謹慎??"},{"pid":"24c0813e61e812a116572ddf68a082bbd913fbe3","tid":2422239,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:10:46.000Z","msg":"又響度扯貓尾 <br />\n收皮啦仆街"},{"pid":"3c6207e39db447525c31510d91fae965db802981","tid":2422239,"uid":54959,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"連對沖都搞咁撚耐都唔掂，你就知無行"},{"pid":"ae60b4957bc8